ZH: 我需要一袋面粉做蛋糕。
EN: I need a bag of flour to make a cake.

ZH: 妈妈说我们家的面粉用完了。
EN: Mom said we ran out of flour at home.

ZH: 面粉是不可少的厨房食材。
EN: Flour is an essential ingredient in the kitchen.

ZH: 昨天我买了一包面粉。
EN: I bought a bag of flour yesterday.

ZH: 面粉的味道总是让人觉得温暖。
EN: The smell of flour always makes people feel warm.

ZH: 没有面粉我们就无法做面包了。
EN: We can't make bread without flour.

ZH: 这家面粉品质很好。
EN: The quality of this flour is very good.

ZH: 我在超市找到了最便宜的面粉。
EN: I found the cheapest flour at the supermarket.

ZH: 他的蛋糕用的面粉是有机的。
EN: His cake is made with organic flour.

ZH: 面粉存放在密封容器里可以保持新鲜。
EN: Flour stored in a sealed container can stay fresh.

ZH: 这袋面粉用完了得赶紧买新的。
EN: This bag of flour is running out and needs to be replaced.

ZH: 面粉包装上有生产日期和保质期。
EN: The packaging of flour has the production date and shelf life.

ZH: 面粉可以用来做面条、馒头和煎饼。
EN: Flour can be used to make noodles, steamed buns, and pancakes.

ZH: 面粉需要慢慢搅拌成面团。
EN: Flour needs to be slowly stirred into dough.

ZH: 蛋糕的秘诀在于选用好的面粉。
EN: The secret to a good cake lies in using good flour.

ZH: 面粉的价钱因品牌和原料而有差异。
EN: The price of flour varies by brand and ingredients.

ZH: 面粉是许多烹饪食谱的基础。
EN: Flour is the foundation of many cooking recipes.

ZH: 妈妈说我们家的面粉是从农场直接购买的。
EN: Mom said our flour at home is bought directly from the farm.

ZH: 这种面粉不含有防腐剂。
EN: This flour does not contain preservatives.

ZH: 面粉的营养价值很高。
EN: Flour has high nutritional value.
